com.cboe.interfaces.domain.property.PropertyDefinition
public class PropertyDefinitionImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.cboe.interfaces.domain.property.PropertyDefinition

The definition for a Property. This class contains all the elements that define what a specific property can do. The name of the definition is specified in the property, to tie them together.
